{"_id":"HTAcro01h","name":"Acrobatics","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Master of movement in tight spaces.","description":"<p>+2 to Mobility when moving through a Cluttered or Cramped zone, or performing a controlled jump.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTAnal01h","name":"Analytical","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Logic over instinct — read people with your mind.","description":"<p>Roll Insight using Wits instead of Empathy when detecting lies or sensing someone's emotions.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTAsas01h","name":"Assassin","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Close the distance before they know you're there.","description":"<p>When attempting a sneak attack, no -2 modifier when moving to Engaged range.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTBody01h","name":"Bodyguard","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Take the hit so they don't have to.","description":"<p>When someone within Short range is hit, roll Mobility to take the hit instead. You can push the roll.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTCalm01h","name":"Calming Presence","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Your presence alone steadies shattered nerves.","description":"<p>Once per Turn, reduce another character's Stress Level by one within Short range. Must be in a safe place. Cannot use on yourself.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTComp01h","name":"Compassion","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Push beyond your limits when others need you most.","description":"<p>Push any skill roll based on Empathy twice, not just once.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTCrea01h","name":"Creative","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"You find solutions where others see only walls.","description":"<p>Once per session, automatically pass one Observation roll without rolling. GM has final say.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTDodg01h","name":"Dodge","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Roll out of the way — even from monsters.","description":"<p>When attacked in close combat, dodge using Mobility instead of Melee. Can only reduce damage. Works against creatures.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTDriv01h","name":"Driver","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Pedal to the metal, whatever the road.","description":"<p>+2 to Mobility when driving a vehicle.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTFast01h","name":"Fast Reflexes","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Always first to act when it all goes wrong.","description":"<p>Draw two initiative cards instead of one. Choose the one you want to use.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTFiel01h","name":"Field Surgeon","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Steady hands between life and death.","description":"<p>+1 to Healing when treating someone who is about to die from a critical injury.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTFlyw01h","name":"Flyweight","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Speed and agility beat raw power.","description":"<p>When blocking in close combat, use Agility instead of Strength.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTGrap01h","name":"Grappler","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Once you have them, they're not going anywhere.","description":"<p>+2 to Melee rolls made to grapple a target.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTGutF01h","name":"Gut Feeling","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Something's wrong — you feel it before you see it.","description":"<p>Roll Observation using Empathy instead of Wits to detect an approaching threat.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTHard01h","name":"Hardened","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Your mind has seen too much to break easily.","description":"<p>Maximum Resolve increased by 1. Can be taken up to three times.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTHeal01h","name":"Healer","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Your body mends faster than most.","description":"<p>The healing time of critical injuries is halved for you.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTHrdH01h","name":"Hard Hitter","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Wind up and hit like a freight train.","description":"<p>+1 to Melee if you sacrifice your fast action in the round.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTInqu01h","name":"Inquisitive","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Push your mind further than others dare.","description":"<p>Push any skill roll based on Wits twice, not just once.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTJab001h","name":"Jab","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Strike fast, even if it costs you.","description":"<p>Make a melee weapon attack as a fast action at a -2 modification.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTKill01h","name":"Killer","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"You know exactly where to strike.","description":"<p>When an enemy sustains a critical injury, roll twice and choose the result you want.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTLgSl01h","name":"Light Sleeper","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"A few hours and you're ready to go again.","description":"<p>Only need to sleep one shift every two days instead of one shift every day.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTLght01h","name":"Light Eater","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"You need less than most to keep going.","description":"<p>When making a supply roll for food, roll two fewer dice (minimum one).</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTLogi01h","name":"Logical","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"A well-reasoned argument beats charm every time.","description":"<p>Roll Persuasion using Wits instead of Empathy when convincing someone to see your point of view.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTLuck01h","name":"Lucky","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Somehow, you always walk away.","description":"<p>When you suffer a critical injury, re-roll the dice and choose the result you prefer.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTMart01h","name":"Martial Artist","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Precision and speed over brute force.","description":"<p>When making an armed attack in close combat, use Agility instead of Strength.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTMena01h","name":"Menacing","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Your presence is enough of a threat.","description":"<p>Roll Persuasion using Strength instead of Empathy when threatening someone.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTMerc01h","name":"Merciless","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"No hesitation when the moment comes.","description":"<p>Perform a coup de grace without rolling for Empathy.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTMusi01h","name":"Musician","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Music opens doors that nothing else can.","description":"<p>+1 to Persuasion when singing or playing an instrument is helpful. GM has final say.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTOccu01h","name":"Occult Experience","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"You've seen enough of the darkness to stop fearing it.","description":"<p>Do not make a Panic Roll when confronting or witnessing supernatural monsters or events.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTPack01h","name":"Pack Mule","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"You can carry more than anyone expects.","description":"<p>Carry limit increased by +2.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTQuik01h","name":"Quick Draw","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Your weapon is in your hand before they blink.","description":"<p>Draw your weapon without it costing an action.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTRapF01h","name":"Rapid Fire","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"A trigger finger that doesn't quit.","description":"<p>Fire a pistol or rifle as a fast action at a -2 modification.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTRapR01h","name":"Rapid Reload","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Empty and loaded before they notice.","description":"<p>Reload a weapon as a fast action instead of a slow action.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTReck01h","name":"Reckless","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Impulsiveness can be a weapon too.","description":"<p>Push any skill roll based on Agility twice, not just once.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTSeco01h","name":"Second Wind","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Not dead yet — roll to prove it.","description":"<p>When broken, roll Stamina to regain Health or Resolve. Cannot push. Once per broken state. No effect against critical injuries.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTSnip01h","name":"Sniper","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"One shot, one kill — from where they can't see you.","description":"<p>+1 to Marksmanship when firing a single shot at Long range or more from a hidden position.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTToug01h","name":"Tough","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"You absorb punishment that would floor anyone else.","description":"<p>Maximum Health increased by 1. Can be taken up to three times.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTTrGr01h","name":"True Grit","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Sheer determination pushes past your limits.","description":"<p>Push any skill roll based on Strength twice, not just once.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTWatc01h","name":"Watchful","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Eyes in the back of your head.","description":"<p>+2 to Observation when trying to spot a sneak attack.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HTWeap01h","name":"Weapon Specialist","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"excerpt":"Trained to perfection with your weapon of choice.","description":"<p>Expert with one weapon type. +1 when using that type. Can be chosen multiple times, including unarmed.</p>","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}
